{"tid":1901770,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"陳茂波：警隊加班「相當辛苦」　發放加班津貼是「應該」、「合理」","createTime":"2020-02-28T04:12:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-28T14:43:53.000Z","uid":212626,"like":12,"dislike":570,"uniUserReply":108,"replies":[{"pid":"1943114661ca8cbc26a806bbb213846f096c0320","tid":1901770,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T04:12:35.000Z","msg":"財政司司長陳茂波出席立法會財委會簡介《預算案》，民主派議員表示，《預算案》牽涉警隊開支增至258億元，香港人會很警覺，建議陳茂波應該將1萬元派錢計劃分拆。<br />\n<br />\n陳茂波回應指出，派錢撥款和警隊資源是風馬牛不相及，批評民主派指控不合理，以偏概全，混淆視聽。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">他又強調，警隊處理暴力場面加班相當辛苦，發放加班津貼是應該，亦是按立法會的授權進行，而警方總結經驗，認為要補充人手和裝備是合理</span>。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2387554/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2387554%2F&d=d7tjXuyQMlDyBW65i2Gj0ZB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=dbf2620d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2387554/</a>"},{"pid":"3d349a42643b04ab50f24ad6beebf6508cf2afe5","tid":1901770,"uid":268519,"like":28,"dislike":4,"score":24,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T04:15:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OqM5iNW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOqM5iNW.jpg&h=b6410e6e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1fd4d2171bcc9364d3e79492dd9af062f828b7b7","tid":1901770,"uid":136115,"like":45,"dislike":1,"score":44,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T04:15:10.000Z","msg":"屌出聲，條數點計都計唔到啦 督數話合理?"},{"pid":"ed2d31cc3bf511bc20ac735371c6f505c385524d","tid":1901770,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T04:16:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6fd25aff34cef71166ea9cfa6111f985daae6db","tid":1901770,"uid":212626,"like":135,"dislike":3,"score":132,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-02-28T04:19:52.000Z","msg":"雙重標準到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n醫護唔辛苦咩<img src=\"/ass